results.shortDescription: Don takes a deeper look at his life after he investigates the circumstances surrounding an ex-girlfriend's death.

As the pressure of his job mounts, Don recognizes the impact his professional life has on his personal life, and he decides to investigate his flirtation with AUSA Robin Brooks.
